game.name: Catch to Animals
game.description:
Like many others, you want to be with your favorite animals to enjoy in your own style. We respect the feelings of each gamer and, as a response, we have got you covered with a brand new action-packed challenge where a horde of animals are waiting for you. Would you like to try it out to kill your time? Join Catch to Animals and get ready to have the best time online under a horde of colorful creatures! Your catching abilities will be tested here in this arcade fun challenge. 
Make sure to keep your eyes glued to the screen and put your fingers on the mouse or tap the screen on mobile phone not to miss even a single shot. Be careful as you would have only three lives to use in this html5 shooting game! You will lose your game immediately if all you run out of all your three lives. Animals will keep falling down on the screen and you as a player have to click on them to catch and send them to their destination. 
Once your game is over, you can track your best and present score on the screen. Try to catch as many animals as you possible to create your new best score in this animal mobile game! No worries if you lose as you can restart your game and enter the animal catching fun again as many times as you want. We cover a wide collection of animal games for kids that are playable on multiple devices, including desktops, mobile phones, tablets and iPads or iPhones. Enjoy more games online without download on atmegame.com!
